73→brain — Connect coding agents to the Brain knowledge graph
74→
75→Usage:
76→  brain init                     Set up workspace auth and git hooks
77→  brain system load-context      Load project context (SessionStart hook)
78→  brain system set-project <id>  Set project for current directory
79→  brain system check-updates     Check for graph updates (UserPromptSubmit hook)
80→  brain system end-session       End agent session (SessionEnd hook)
81→  brain check-commit             Pre-commit hook: check for task completion
